DSCI Recruitment 2025 - Walk - in interview for 41 Senior Resident Posts
Harshitha / All Government Jobs / Aug 25, 2025, 09:44 IST
 Chittaranjan National Cancer Institute
 41 Jobs |  Posted On : 25-Aug-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 67,700 to 67,700




FOLLOW

The Delhi State Cancer Institute (DSCI) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 41 Senior Resident Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS, Diploma, DNB, MD/MS, and Post-graduation can apply for the DSCI Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application fee, salary, and how to apply for these posts before the deadline. The application dates have already begun.




If you are more interested in Government Jobs, candidates can also apply for jobs in Delhi.

DSCI Recruitment 2025 Eligiblity Criteria:
Name of the Posts	Vacancies	Education
Senior Resident	41	MBBS, Diploma, MD/MS, Post-graduation, DNB.

DSCI Recruitment 2025 Age Limit:

The minimum age limit: 21 Years.
The maximum age limit: 45 Years.
Age relaxation is based on the Organisation's norms.

DSCI Recruitment 2025 Selection Process:

The selection process is based on the interview.

DSCI Recruitment 2025 Application Fee:

There is no application fee.

DSCI Recruitment 2025 Pay Scale:

The basic pay: Rs. 67,700/- per month.
How to Apply for the DSCI Recruitment 2025:
Go to the official website.
Visit the DSCI Recruitment 2025 notification.
Read the instructions carefully and check the eligiblity criteria.
If you are eligible.
Gather all the required documents to the filled application form.
Carry all the required documents to the interview.
Attend the interview at the mentioned address.

Address:

The Director’s Office at DSCISCI (East).

Important Dates:

Starting date	21-08-2025
Closing date	27-08-2025
